To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Minimum _min;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_min = MIN(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_min.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "minimum", _min.Current.Value);
}
